## Product reviews

You can add product reviews to the product page by [utilizing the Timeline (VX) widget](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_timeline-vx-widget_.md) with the selected mode **Current post reviews**

Reviews can be limited to customers only (completed order), by editing your **Products CPT  General  Reviews  Allow post reviews  From customers only**
